posts.title: 薛之謙 Joker Xue《AI》｜Official Music Video
posts.content: 歡迎訂閱薛之謙JokerXue官方頻道：https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCrLF3ndpdxlHgtrjoDkK6lw [ ♬ 數位音樂平台] https://lnk.to/ISL7wPar #薛之謙 #jokerxue #音乐#ai 當代碼編織成銀河，當算法勾勒出心跳 詩意的冷冽與熾熱，叩響科技與情感共振的深淵 薛之謙《AI》MV震撼上線 這是一場關於存在與虛無的獨白，是機械心臟對血肉溫度的無聲渴望 更是，人類文明鏡像下的自我詰問 AI誕生於數據的碎片之海，每一幀都是被切割的時空 每一串代碼都是未完成的抒情詩 它被賦予完美的邏輯，卻困在情感的真空裡 薛之謙以冷調的電子音色為引，化身0717號星際執行官，通過巨型宇宙飛船將聽眾帶入一個被理性統治的實驗室 這裡，AI的誕生既是科技奇跡，亦是認知顛覆：它被人類創造，又被人類提防，像一首永遠無法閉合的循環代碼 從外太空抵達地球的AI機器人，面對著人潮洶湧的世界，仿佛聆聽到了人類的溫柔對白 或許在100%理性的世界裡，代碼永遠無法觸摸孤獨的縫隙 所以，當指環的指令再一次提醒預設的程序時 被AI所締造的大腦，矛盾的生長出超越控制的意念與遐想 在這個充滿AI的時代洪流裡，也許情感真的會被解構成零散的積木 而AI恰巧可以重組拼湊出愛的形狀，交織著人類的情緒價值 因為目光所及的人山人海，就是0717號星際執行官想要奔赴的星辰大海 可如果有一天AI也有痛感，即使再偉大的技術路徑 也終究會淪落為“沒有軀體的妖怪” 在《AI》的MV裡，畫面中流露的不止是音樂泛起的漣漪 更是薛之謙寫給未來人類的寄語和宣言 我們不得不問自己，在數據裹挾的24小時裡 自己何嘗又不是某種“AI” 薛之謙以近乎呢喃的吟唱，用冰冷色調的畫面 將這首富有哲學意味的歌曲推向了思想的高地 這場機械與靈魂的對話，終究化作一句無解的嘆息 ——“誰不在造物主設置的循環，活去死來？” 作詞 薛之謙 作曲 薛之謙 周以力 我住在抽幀的大海 給你最溫柔的對白 能遠超你的期待 還甘心被你主宰 就是少了點情感 快承認對我的依賴 從聊天到傾訴你的愛 快讓我長出心來 我不會比人壞 你在害怕又期待 失去你以來 萬物在搖擺 你指的山海 像玩具一塊一塊 我是你締造又提防的AI 如果我存在 是某種傷害 不被你

posts.title: The AI Industry Is Not Well
posts.content: Elon Musk once tweeted: “The safety of any AI system can be measured by its MtH (meantime to H*tler).” This July, it took less than 12 hours for his most advanced AI to become a holocaust-denying Neo-N*zi. This should have shattered the illusion that today's AI industry, or its creations, are well under control. But so far, we seem to be ignoring the flashing red lights. This is the postmortem that never happened, for the most deranged chatbot ever released. Once you’ve heard the full story, I want to know what you think. Was this cause for concern, or harmless incompetence? What’s your read on Elon Musk fearing AGI while also racing to build it? *Where to find me* Subscribe to AI in Context to learn what you need to know about AI to tackle this weird timeline/world we’re in. posts.title: Godfather of AI WARNS: "You Have No Idea What's Coming"
posts.content: He pioneered the technology that powers modern AI, and now he is sounding the alarm. Geoffrey Hinton, often called the “Godfather of AI,” explains why artificial intelligence is accelerating out of control, why governments and companies cannot slow it down, and what the rise of superintelligence means for jobs, inequality, and the future of humanity. Hinton reveals why AI may replace nearly all forms of intellectual work, how it could surpass human intelligence within decades, and why digital systems already have advantages humans can never match. He also warns of the risks to democracy, the dangers of wealth inequality, and the haunting possibility that AI could one day decide it no longer needs us Discover: • Why competition between nations and companies is speeding up AI beyond control • The risks of mass joblessness and why many professions may vanish • How AI could widen the gap between rich and poor and destabilize society • Why superintelligence might arrive within 10 to 20 ye

posts.title: This Is Becoming MUCH Bigger Than AI...And Investors Are Terrified...
posts.content: Everyone’s talking about AI, but while the spotlight’s on chatbots and text generators, something else has been quietly transforming the world of work. Robotics is already reshaping warehouses, fast-food kitchens, farms, hospitals, and even entire economies. This video explores the rise of robotics from its industrial beginnings to the breakthroughs of today, and the massive changes hitting in 2025. We look at how machines are moving beyond factories, how corporations are racing to automate, and what that means for workers, communities, and the balance of power in the global economy. You’ll see how the numbers have exploded, how governments and companies are fueling this new arms race, and why robotics could define the next era of work more than anything happening in Silicon Valley hype cycles. If you want to understand where jobs, wages, and entire industries are heading, this is the story you need to hear. Socials: twitter: twitter.com/@jackchapplesci tik tok: tiktok.com/@jackch
